{
 "name": "RPlog_Into_the_Trap",
 "title": "Into the Trap",
 "summary": "The captured Jedi Jessalyn Valios, battered from a recent duel with the Dark Lady, is escorted into the Sith-relic-filled trophy hall of the Sith Valak. Greeting her with mocking courtesy in his temple, Valak declares there will be no terms and reveals that the ancient Sith artifact she unwittingly delivered to him is the missing piece of a trap designed to freeze her life force. As he brings the two glowing pieces together, Jessalyn hurls her guards aside with the Force and bolts for the exit, but the guards cross their force pikes to block her path. A lance of blue lightning catches her between the shoulder blades, and she collapses, rigid and senseless -- destined to become another preserved trophy of the Dark Side in Valak collection.",
